      "text": "Vera Stepanova\nVera is a beautiful blonde, a longhaired, young Russian woman who escaped from the Soviet Union and immigrated to the United States in 1984. She now lives in New York City and works as a nurse at St. Jude's Hospital. She used to be in love with Aston Lockwood who broke off their relationship to turn to the United States on urgent business before the Cold War. \n\nShe has secretly hired a group of criminals to attend a party hosted by the Lockwoods (Brutus Sampson, and Edward Cass) and is intent on destroying the Lockwood family legacy. She ignores Hugo Lockwood though he is in love with her. She is also very fond of her dog, Pasha, who she says is like a son to her. ",
