      "text": "30 Years old. Works as a researcher for the New York Times, and has lived in Italy, and France during his days at college. He is engaged to Amber Miah, a photographer. He is the son of Royce Lockwood and Lillian Lockwood. Sigmund Lockwood is Aston's grandfather. \nHe and Vera were in a committed relationship for almost a year while he was away in Italy and France, and he had to break it of when he received an urgent summons from his father after the crash of the Russian Spy Satellite Cosmos 1402 and the panic that gripped the world around the nuclear threat. \nAfter years apart He and Vera are on different life paths and Vera has not found love since.\nHe is Hugo Lockwood's older brother. \nBrutus is Aston's Friend from college in Europe.",
