      "text": "A 25 Years old socialite. Terminally single rich young man. He is secretly in love with Amber Miah, his brother's fiance. He is the son of Royce Lockwood and Lillian Lockwood. Sigmund Lockwood is Hugo's grandfather. \nHe used to be in love with Vera Stepanova, who he met while visiting his brother in France before the satellites fell and Aston returned home alone. He was unable to contact Vera due to the Cold War and has hated Aston ever since. It is his purpose to ruin any good thing that Aston does. He is a stout and rugged man with short black hair and brown eyes. Hugo is described as living in Aston's shadow, and he seeks attention from his parents by getting into trouble.",
