      "text": "Christopher Lockwood is Royce Lockwood's brother and Aston's Uncle. He is 48 years old in 1987 when he disappears from a party in the family mansion in Colorado under mysterious circumstances. He has blonde hair that is slightly longer than it should be but his piercing blue eyes distract anyone that cares about his hair. He is sent back in time and trapped there. He must try to find a way to escape. He tries everything and even writes messages in first editions of books that he knows are on his shelf in the future.\n\nHe has conflict with Lillian because of some comments that he made about her when they were younger and she was dating his brother. He thought she was in it for the money and said so to the family.",
