      "text": "Auralee Rosé, or Aurora, is a beautiful French woman with long blonde hair and blue eyes. She has a mysterious past, and she appears to be on the run from some sort of criminal organization. She's also a talented singer. She often wears a black dress with a red scarf, and she carries a pocketbook. She is so beautiful that she becomes the center of attention anywhere she goes and is entertaining flirtatious relationships with Christopher, Edward, and keeping Hugo at arms length. She has tension with Lillian because Lillian can see through her seductive charm. \nThere is something about her that is not quite right, but it could be in my imagination.",
