      "text": "As the story goes, the ancient Egyptian God Anubis was born from the womb of Isis when she sacrificed her son Osiris. In doing so, she gave him his immortality. This event became a symbol for the rebirth of a new beginning. It marked the point where the past becomes the present and the future. As such, many cultures around the world revere the god. Some see him as a guardian of tombs, while others view him as an advisor to pharaohs and kings throughout Egypt during the dynastic period. In reality he is just a man. A man from another time.  Tesla, Marconi, Einstein, and the Elijah Thril Machine all culminated in the story of one man.  Displaced in time.  And this time...was not our time.  The year? Well we don't know exactly because the only record left us are the notes and diagrams of the original inventor.  What we do have, though, were the records found in the tomb of King Tutankhamun. These papers contained the secrets of how to make an exobiotic machine.\nThe word \"exo\" means outside or beyond, whereas \"biotics,\" meaning life, describes what happens within living organisms—the biosphere. When you combine them together, you get the term exobiological, referring to any biological entity that exists in outer space. But there must be something more to the equation than meets the eye. Something far greater. For instance, did they really find evidence of alien beings inside of the walls of King Tutankhamun's burial chamber back in 1922?\nWhat if the Egyptians weren't alone after all?  Could it be possible their civilization wasn't destroyed as ours will soon become, instead they went underground and moved on to the next phase of existence?  \nDr. Jules Dufour, a scientist working under the French government's research facility called L'Institut Français de Recherche pour l'Explication des Phénomènes Nuclés (IFREPN), had been searching through old documents stored deep beneath Paris, France. While looking over some of the files, he stumbled across several pages detailing experiments conducted by Nikola Tesla between 1899-1903. His name seemed familiar to him. Then again, everyone knew about him even if they didn't realize it. After all, Tesla invented alternating current electricity, which allowed power plants to produce large amounts of energy. However, Tesla also made other discoveries along the way, including the induction motor and radio transmission. Unfortunately, these accomplishments never reached widespread popularity. Instead, Tesla disappeared into obscurity until his death in 1943. Or did he die then? \nExoBacter Papers - Declaration One. The Rite of Blood Harvest\nIt is our right as citizens of the world to harvest. \nIt is our right as earthbound peoples of every bloodline to maintain our heritage. \nIt is our right to explore the domains of time for our benefit. \nThis paper shall serve as a declaration of my intent and purpose regarding the rite of harvesting. I am Dr. Guglielmo Marconi, born March 3rd, 1890 in Venice, Italy. My family line traces its lineage back hundreds of generations with ties to the Venetian Republic, where we were once free people. We were able to live freely without fear because of the respect and reverence shown toward us by the ruling classes. Our ancestors fought long and hard against the oppression of others so that we might have peace and freedom here on Earth. I was given the opportunity to become an ExoBacter on a winter day in 1889 when the wind blew cold over the Atlantic ocean. I met the future in a moment and was transported to our time 2098. I put my faith in the ExoBacter Council and believe in their vision for our destiny. I have been asked to write out the rites of the harvest for the people. It would be an honor for me to do this. This document serves as a testament to those who come after, as well as myself, to ensure that no one forgets what must be done. With Elijah Thril's Temporal Shift Mechanism the public became time-free. For the first time in history, we have access to the past. ExoBacters believe that we have a right to the minds of history as a kind of eminent domain. In order to preserve ourselves and our culture, it becomes necessary to collect the knowledge contained within the memories of humanity. By collecting human memory, we can better understand the universe around us. To protect the sanctity of the planet, it will be imperative that we control how information flows through the network. Therefore, it behooves us to take advantage of the technology already at hand to keep the flow under tight control. The goal of this paper is twofold. First, to provide the general population of mankind (including you) with a detailed description of the rite of harvesting. Second, to establish the legal framework for governing the harvesting process while ensuring that the system does not fall into disarray. As part of the rite of harvesting, each person participating should submit themselves to a full medical examination to verify identity. Once verified, participants may undergo the following procedure to gain enhanced genetics via the transfer of DNA and neural patterns. After completion of the harvest, all harvested individuals will receive the same genetic make-up as the original donor. However, due to changes in the environment, lifestyle choices, and other factors, the individual will possess different personality traits and abilities than their ancestor. These differences will manifest in subtle ways throughout your life. Your descendants will inherit these unique characteristics. If the recipient chooses, he or she may choose whether to pass along the uniqueness to their children. You cannot change the way that you look or act based on the genetics received during the procedure, but you could potentially experience new senses, skills, and even talents that you never had before. All harvested subjects shall be required to sign a waiver agreeing that the harvesting ceremony and subsequent genetic alteration are irreversible. A copy of the consent form must accompany the application to participate in the harvest.\nThis ritual requires the participation of many generations. We need to gather samples over hundreds if not thousands of years so that we may create the ultimate version of ourselves. Each generation of volunteers needs to be carefully chosen according to the specific requirements of the next step. The selection criteria include age, sex, race, ethnicity, geographical origin, etc. When the proper candidate emerges, the family lineages will be traced back to find a suitable ancestor. Then, using modern techniques such as DNA sequencing, the exact genetic makeup of that ancestor shall be compared against the desired trait. The rite of blood harvest has been declared. \n—From \"The Rites Of Harvest,\" a document written by the Modern Marconi Company\n",
